    "JHEP04(2024)048This OPE behaviour corresponds to [15] e ± 1 2 (iq1 +iq 2) V w m 1,m 2 (x; z) ↔ [|Φ ± w ⟩] σ w, (3.12)where this time m 1 and m 2 satisfy (3.6).",
    "Physical correlation functionsAt present, a full discussion of the structure of physical correlation functions of the k = 1 string requires studying the theory as an N = 4 topological string [23,31].",
